import React from "react";

function Icon() {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
      width="40"
      height="40"
      fill="none"
      viewBox="0 0 40 40"
    >
      <path fill="url(#pattern0)" d="M0 0H40V40H0z"></path>
      <defs>
        <pattern
          id="pattern0"
          width="1"
          height="1"
          patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
        >
          <use transform="scale(.00662)" xlinkHref="#image0"></use>
        </pattern>
        <image
          id="image0"
          width="151"
          height="151"
          xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"
        ></image>
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
}

export default Icon;
